{"id":876823,"date":[{"year":1992,"month":7,"day":27}],"page":"5","source":"","region":"","masthead":"笔会","special_issue":"笔会","column":"","genre":"","count":"79","ytitle":"","mtitle":"七绝二首","ftitle":"","authors":["蒋守泉"],"text":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"(一)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棒棰岛边望遗篇，遥忆魏武数挥鞭。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一曲歌舞人散处，何人横槊吟赋归。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"(二)"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清幽茫茫富春江，夜枕江流人大荒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一丈新潮钱塘去，谁识消涓是金钢!"}]}